    "Because the difference between the two datasets is feature-less, this broadening is the same on the classifier training and test datasets.",
    "At the same time, Fig. 15 and Eq.",
    "( 6) illustrate the benefit of studying the weight distributions: the AUC evaluated on the test dataset is stable at 0.5 during the entire training, but the weight distribution shows that the classifier is moving away from optimality.",
